    <p>Ludappex LLC ("we", "our", or "us") operates the mobile game Run, Ozzy, Run! This policy explains how we handle information when you use our app.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not directly collect personal information. However, our app uses third-party services that may collect information:</p>
