    <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>The app saves game progress (score, distance, lives) locally on your device using device storage. This data is not transmitted to our servers.</p>

    <h2>4. Certificate Download</h2>
    <p>Players who complete the full 5000 km journey may download a certificate image. This image is saved directly to your device's gallery and is not uploaded to any server.</p>

    <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our app is suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

    <h2>6. Advertising</h2>
    <p>Our app displays ads via Google AdMob. These ads may be personalized based on your interests. You can opt out of personalized ads in your device settings.</p>

